content: tomguluson92: Merged 10 PRs this month, with significant contributions including a new Text to 3D function in PR #1446 (+3607/-2018 lines), client-github retry functionality in PR #1425 (+2273/-1698 lines), and comprehensive documentation updates in PR #1196 (+23076/-17974 lines). Also made several smaller fixes including environment spelling corrections (#787), UUID compatibility improvements (#785), and Tavily API upgrades (#1246). Activity was occasional throughout the month, with contributions spanning both code improvements (70%) and documentation enhancements (15%).
